high_descs: Turn right head to the table stand in between the fridge and table
Pick up the egg
Turn right walk straight then go to the cabinet across the room
Open the cabinet put the egg on the plate
Pick up the plate with egg then close the cabinet
Turn left facing the extended counter
Put the plate with egg on the right side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with egg on the counter sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter, then hang a right and walk over to the round wooden table.
Pick up the egg off of the round wooden table.
Turn right and walk across the room, the hang a right and walk over to the counter to the left of the sink and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the rightmost upper cabinet in front of you and put the egg on the plate inside.
Pick up the plate with the egg on it out of the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the plate with the egg on it on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with an egg on it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the round table in the left corner of the room.
Pick up the egg to the left of the coffee maker on the table.
Turn to your right and go past the refrigerator, then turn to your right again and go to the top cabinet, to the left of the sink.
Open the cabinet and place the egg on the plate, that is on the bottom left shelf of the cabinet.
Remove the plate with the egg on it from the cabinet.
Turn to your right and go to the counter top to the right of the sink.
Place the plate with the egg on top of it on the counter top to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing an egg on the counter.
